  <brief_title>Study of the Relative Abuse Potential of Acurox Tablets in Non-Dependent Recreational Opioid Users</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo- and Active-Controlled Study to Assess the Relative Abuse Potential of Acurox Tablets in Non-Dependent Recreational Opioid Users</official_title>
