  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to compare the relative abuse potential of two
      different doses of orally administered Acurox Tablets to orally administered
      immediate-release (IR) oxycodone HCl tablets in non-dependent recreational opioid users.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
